com.google.javascript.jscomp.newtypes

Class Declaration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.javascript.jscomp.newtypes.Declaration

  • public class Declaration
extends Object
    Represents a declaration of a javascript type.

    See checkValid() for invariants on a declaration's state. In most cases, only one of the instance fields can be non null.
